<p class="h1">KIRIATH-ARBA</p>
<p class="fl">Ancient name of Hebron, near which is the cave of Machpelah, the burial place of the patriarchs (<a href="?bref=Gen.23.2">Gn 23:2</a>; <a href="?bref=Josh.14.15">Jos 14:15</a>; <a href="?bref=Judg.1.10">Jgs 1:10</a>). <span class="ital">See</span> <a href="?item=HebronPlace_Article_TyndaleOpenBibleDictionary">Hebron (Place) #1</a>.</p>
